data.description: This quiet and serene property is nestled amidst lush greenery, far from the hustle and bustle of city life. A charming home sits at the heart of the property, its warm, inviting ambiance inviting you to unwind and connect with nature. The front porch is new with ample room for furniture to sit and enjoy the fresh country air. Open concept kitchen with island overlooking to living room. Additionally you can enjoy a family gathering in the flex room, family or possibly could be a game room.
